snippet.title: Mario & Sonic at the Rio 2016 Olympic Games (Nintendo 3DS) Playthrough Part 2
snippet.description:
In this part, we get a gold medal in the remaining regular Olympic events and do a few Plus ones.

These are the events shown in this video:

Boxing
Table Tennis
Beach Volleyball
Equestrian
BMX
Rhythmic Gymnastics
Football Plus
Golf Plus
100m Dash Plus
